You can change the text color of a label by setting it as a UIColor, like you would do with shapes.

image::labelTextColor/labelTextColor.png["Label Text Color",height=500]

Text Color
----------
The `textColor` property of a C4Label can be set like so:

[source]
----
label.textColor = C4BLUE;
----